Sa ibang lugar tayo mag-usap.

52
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,480
Huwag kang mag-alala.

53
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:56,599
Maghintay tayo

54
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,680
ilang araw.

55
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,160
Shen Hao,

56
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,160
