72
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,600
Hindi mo pa natatapos ang inumin mo.

73
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,880
saan ka pupunta

74
00:05:53,681 --> 00:05:56,281
Kailangan mo bang gawin ito?

75
